**@apply** — Inline Tailwind utility classes into custom CSS.
```css
.btn {
  @apply px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg;
}
```
Compiles utility classes into standard CSS properties.

**@tailwind** — Inject Tailwind layers into your stylesheet.
```css
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;
```
Each directive injects the corresponding layer of generated styles.

**@layer** — Add custom styles to a Tailwind layer.
```css
@layer components {
  .card { @apply rounded-lg shadow-md p-6; }
}
```
Ensures correct ordering and purge behavior.
